
  Roselia    Grass Type Pokémon

  ROSELIA shoots sharp thorns 
  as projectiles at any opponent 
  that tries to steal the flowers 
  on its arms.  The aroma of this 
  Pokémon brings serenity to living 
  things. 
	   Evolution Chain
  Budew ► Roselia ► Roserade

